main event: A civilian observer sighted three objects flying in formation over Vashon, Washington on September 13, 1965.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 20 seconds.
No further data or physical evidence was obtained.
The report was part of the Project Blue Book investigation into unidentified flying objects (UFOs).
The observer expressed long-standing interest in UFO reports and requested more information from the Project Blue Book program.
The observer promised to keep any provided information confidential at the request of the U.S. government.
